      • ConnectionData

        public ConnectionData(Host host1,
                      Host host2,
                      java.lang.String username,
                      java.lang.String password,
                      int portVPN)
        Connection data used to generate the port forwarding
        Parameters:
        host1 - - This host is used for the port forwarding, The username and password are used to get access to this host
        host2 - - Host where the connection is redirected
        username - - Username to get access to host1
        password - - Password to get access to host1
        portVPN - - Port used for the local redirection
